{"tid":374123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]孤狼式炸彈刀手襲大球場　反恐特勤隊出撃制服","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T06:53:17.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94fe55b25b8870fdca373a1ab1a50e3191dd9748","tid":374123,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791687/xlarge/4f69954cc8abd4a3324c9acc98c785f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791687%2Fxlarge%2F4f69954cc8abd4a3324c9acc98c785f6.jpg&h=fc89fd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆炸過後，觀眾大逃亡，傷者倒地待救。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791874/xlarge/390e3a61e7c4027ddb65e8bdd0b0f176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791874%2Fxlarge%2F390e3a61e7c4027ddb65e8bdd0b0f176.jpg&h=8a0d62c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">觀眾席下方，兇徒持刀指嚇。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791871/xlarge/6052c94f52ced8a88bd11c330474e549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791871%2Fxlarge%2F6052c94f52ced8a88bd11c330474e549.jpg&h=4f9581b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中間位置，兇徒持刀施襲。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791866/xlarge/32fbe7e3b1976c00e1ef03e23d019eeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791866%2Fxlarge%2F32fbe7e3b1976c00e1ef03e23d019eeb.jpg&h=9f929ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">上方位置，兇徒脅持人質。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791875/xlarge/b0e4897926372e6bd03452ccdd22c15f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791875%2Fxlarge%2Fb0e4897926372e6bd03452ccdd22c15f.jpg&h=455b6c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">CTRU人員制服兇徒。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791872/xlarge/7db079c19d5ec0e22d86af2c858945ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791872%2Fxlarge%2F7db079c19d5ec0e22d86af2c858945ad.jpg&h=81f7e96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">CTRU人員制服兇徒。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791868/xlarge/1c269cc2be78ae5fb1790e6a3000a92b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791868%2Fxlarge%2F1c269cc2be78ae5fb1790e6a3000a92b.jpg&h=3da820e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">拯救傷者。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791869/xlarge/f1ae0323f68f6305573b5276b3ce12b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791869%2Fxlarge%2Ff1ae0323f68f6305573b5276b3ce12b3.jpg&h=8cb134ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">將傷者送離現場。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791867/xlarge/877b67ef03268fd6f6e7648d3b7dc7dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791867%2Fxlarge%2F877b67ef03268fd6f6e7648d3b7dc7dd.jpg&h=99502945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警員持盾戒備。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791870/xlarge/61cfe5e529347c919bf3a0310465b411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791870%2Fxlarge%2F61cfe5e529347c919bf3a0310465b411.jpg&h=6cee7158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">拆彈機械人檢查被撃斃兇徒身上的背心炸彈。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791873/xlarge/9dfa4a403209522f5eef5810a03a80cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791873%2Fxlarge%2F9dfa4a403209522f5eef5810a03a80cd.jpg&h=8c50c1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆炸品處理課人員穿防爆衣拆除炸彈。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791877/xlarge/e9d8d1434f1f614ba716745391f94276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791877%2Fxlarge%2Fe9d8d1434f1f614ba716745391f94276.jpg&h=05690152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆炸品處理課人員檢查觀眾席下方曾爆炸位置。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791876/xlarge/144ac5c2fc391b68a1307626c3992b7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791876%2Fxlarge%2F144ac5c2fc391b68a1307626c3992b7b.jpg&h=44d8ab99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆炸品處理課人員移走背心炸彈。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791879/xlarge/4347481787f429918a62f7facf4ad879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791879%2Fxlarge%2F4347481787f429918a62f7facf4ad879.jpg&h=7128724e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警犬到場搜索。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791878/xlarge/5e11b7503a9e46eec7b16bbc9068f342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791878%2Fxlarge%2F5e11b7503a9e46eec7b16bbc9068f342.jpg&h=579a3f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">消防處救護隊到場協助分流傷者及送院。(鄧栢良攝)</span><br />\n<br />\nCTRU瑞士製半自動步槍SIG 516 CQB<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/791994/xlarge/ba0c73efeb976b2a3475517689e98a6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F791994%2Fxlarge%2Fba0c73efeb976b2a3475517689e98a6a.jpg&h=a64c93c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特勤隊配置的新槍為瑞士製半自動步槍SIG 516 CQB，警方於去年購入。根據資料，SIG 516 由槍械生產商SIG Sauer於2010年開始出產，每分鐘可連續發射750至950發子彈，亦可配合軍用及警用步槍子彈5.56mmX45 NATO，其射程範圍遠超特勤隊過去使用的MP5衝鋒槍，及加裝不同組件如瞄準鏡及槍托等作不同用途。<br />\n<br />\nEOD大型拆彈機械人&mdash;&mdash;威霸龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/792022/xlarge/10665a27c65758459331852f5c95e3c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F792022%2Fxlarge%2F10665a27c65758459331852f5c95e3c4.jpg&h=12fc18a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「威霸龍」重達300公斤，是小型拆彈機械人「獨眼龍」的十倍重量，可處理較大型爆破。它採用履帶裝置，可作全地形行駛，在碎石、沙地、草地上行動自如，及攀爬45度斜坡。它具備三支不同口徑、用作處理簡易爆炸裝置的高壓水炮、七種拆彈武器、一枝散彈槍、機械長臂、防霧攝錄鏡頭等裝置。「威霸龍」可由EOD人員以遙控遠距離進行拆彈工作。<br />\n<br />\nEOD的保護裝備&mdash;&mdash;防爆衣<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/792054/xlarge/130c56312b6ec118f4b1c0f058b9ce54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F792054%2Fxlarge%2F130c56312b6ec118f4b1c0f058b9ce54.jpg&h=5baffe4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整套防爆衣重達70磅，頭盔重約25磅。根據資料，防爆衣手袖設有控制板，以控制頭盔內的散熱扇，除了通風外，亦可清除霧氣以免阻擋視野。頭盔前端設有照明燈，方便在光線不足的環境內工作。防爆衣亦可以降低近距離爆炸造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/114616/-CTRU%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%BC%E5%BC%8F%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E8%A5%B2%E5%A4%A7%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%A4%E9%9A%8A%E5%87%BA%E6%92%83%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F114616%2F-CTRU%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E7%258B%25BC%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2588%2580%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%25A4%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2592%2583%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%258D&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3b3dffe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/114616/-CTRU%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%BC%E5%BC%8F%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E8%A5%B2%E5%A4%A7%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%A4%E9%9A%8A%E5%87%BA%E6%92%83%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D</a>"},{"pid":"cfa1454b5c5838976668c938ebe9d1ee7a3ea8cd","tid":374123,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e10748a44c42a0f4ef4239d62f147bb0489765","tid":374123,"uid":130247,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=81614293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so%2Fsource.gif&h=c6e30b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif&h=f7613e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26FPnpatcd94T0JLW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26FPnpatcd94T0JLW%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b585f810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/5KEXNDz3wuac/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5KEXNDz3wuac%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3743800e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7aPsXPUuzFrJ6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F7aPsXPUuzFrJ6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8c126a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.inii